# NOTE: bin/** is deliberately NOT ignored. `scripts/fetch-llama.mjs <target>`
# stages llama-server + its dylibs there, and shipping them is the entire point
# of the platform-specific VSIX -- excluding bin/ silently produces a targeted
# VSIX with no engine in it, which fails only on a user's machine. The
# untargeted fallback VSIX has no bin/ to begin with, so it needs no rule here.
